The Concerned Nigerians group has called on the United States, United Kingdom and European Union to prevail on the leadership of the Independent National Electoral Commission to ensure the smooth conduct of the governorship election in Edo State. The group, which earlier described the exercise as a coup, further said that there were efforts by politicians to undermine the exercise.  See Also






